etphoneshome.managers

Class FlaskManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • etphoneshome.managers.FlaskManager

  • public class FlaskManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for handling the flasks thrown by the enemies. Using addFlask will add the flask to the arrraylist Using removeFlask will remove the flask from the arraylist Using clearFlasks will remove all the flasks in the arraylist
